<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Penghitung WR MLBB</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        body { background-color: #1a1a22; color: #e2e8f0; }
        .neon-border { border: 1px solid rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.2); box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.05); }
        .input-dark { background-color: #141419; border: 1px solid #2e2e38; }
        .input-dark:focus { border-color: #f97316; outline: none; }
        @keyframes fadeInDown {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        .animate-fade-in { animation: fadeInDown 0.4s ease-out forwards; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="font-sans min-h-screen flex flex-col">

    <!-- NAVBAR KONSISTEN -->
    <nav class="bg-[#111116] border-b border-gray-800 px-8 py-5 flex justify-between items-center sticky top-0 z-50 shadow-2xl">
        <div class="text-orange-500 font-black text-2xl tracking-widest uppercase hover:scale-105 transition transform duration-200">
            <a href="/">[INFO MLBB]</a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex space-x-8 text-md font-bold tracking-wide">
            <a href="/" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-orange-400 transition duration-300">HERO</a>
            <a href="/kalkulator" class="text-orange-400 border-b-2 border-orange-400 pb-1">KALKULATOR</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- CONTAINER UTAMA -->
    <main class="flex-grow flex flex-col items-center pt-8 px-4 pb-12 w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-2 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-2 h-7 bg-orange-500 rounded-sm"></span> Kalkulator <span class="text-orange-500">Win Rate</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs">Pilih mode perhitungan statistik yang kamu butuhkan di bawah ini.</p>
        </div>

        <% if (hasil) { %>
            <div class="mb-10 text-center bg-[#1e1e26] neon-border p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full max-w-2xl animate-fade-in relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-red-600"></div>
                <h2 class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 mb-4 border-b border-gray-800 pb-2 uppercase tracking-widest">Hasil Kalkulasi</h2>
                
                <% if (!input.target_wr) { %>
                    <div class="flex justify-around items-center">
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-1">Total Win</p>
                            <p class="font-black text-orange-400 text-4xl"><%= hasil.totalWin %> <span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-500">Match</span></p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="h-12 w-px bg-gray-800"></div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-1">Total Lose</p>
                            <p class="font-black text-gray-300 text-4xl"><%= hasil.totalLose %> <span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-500">Match</span></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% } else { %>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Untuk mencapai target WR <span class="font-bold text-white"><%= input.target_wr %>%</span>, kamu membutuhkan:</p>
                    <p class="font-black text-orange-500 text-6xl my-2"><%= hasil.neededWinStreak %></p>
                    <p class="text-xs font-bold text-orange-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Win Tanpa Kalah (Win Streak)</p>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        <% } %>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 w-full">
            
            <div class="bg-[#1e1e26] p-8 rounded-2xl neon-border shadow-xl hover:border-orange-500/50 transition duration-300">
                <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-orange-400 mb-1">Cek Win / Lose</h2>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-6">Hitung jumlah pasti kemenangan dan kekalahan dari statistik total match kamu.</p>
                
                <form action="/kalkulator/hitung" method="POST" class="space-y-4">
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-xs font-bold mb-1 text-gray-300 uppercase tracking-wider">Total Match</label>
                        <input type="number" name="total_match" placeholder="Contoh: 1112" value="<%= (!input.target_wr && input.total_match) ? input.total_match : '' %>" required class="input-dark w-full p-3 text-sm text-white rounded-xl transition duration-200">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-xs font-bold mb-1 text-gray-300 uppercase tracking-wider">Total WR Anda (%)</label>
                        <input type="number" step="0.1" name="current_wr" placeholder="Contoh: 90.5" value="<%= (!input.target_wr && input.current_wr) ? input.current_wr : '' %>" required class="input-dark w-full p-3 text-sm text-white rounded-xl transition duration-200">
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="w-full py-3 mt-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-orange-600 hover:from-orange-600 hover:to-orange-700 font-bold rounded-xl text-white text-sm shadow-lg transform active:scale-95 transition duration-200">Hitung Win / Lose</button>
                </form>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-[#1e1e26] p-8 rounded-2xl neon-border shadow-xl hover:border-orange-500/50 transition duration-300">
                <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-orange-400 mb-1">Hitung Target WR</h2>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-6">Prediksi jumlah win streak beruntun yang wajib kamu capai untuk menaikkan win rate.</p>
                
                <form action="/kalkulator/hitung" method="POST" class="space-y-4">
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-xs font-bold mb-1 text-gray-300 uppercase tracking-wider">Total Match</label>
                        <input type="number" name="total_match" placeholder="Contoh: 272" value="<%= (input.target_wr && input.total_match) ? input.total_match : '' %>" required class="input-dark w-full p-3 text-sm text-white rounded-xl transition duration-200">
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-xs font-bold mb-1 text-gray-300 uppercase tracking-wider">WR Saat Ini (%)</label>
                            <input type="number" step="0.1" name="current_wr" placeholder="Contoh: 78.2" value="<%= (input.target_wr && input.current_wr) ? input.current_wr : '' %>" required class="input-dark w-full p-3 text-sm text-white rounded-xl transition duration-200">
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-xs font-bold mb-1 text-gray-300 uppercase tracking-wider">Target WR (%)</label>
                            <input type="number" step="0.1" name="target_wr" placeholder="Contoh: 80" value="<%= input.target_wr || '' %>" required class="input-dark w-full p-3 text-sm text-white rounded-xl transition duration-200 border-b-2 border-orange-500">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="w-full py-3 mt-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-orange-600 hover:from-orange-600 hover:to-orange-700 font-bold rounded-xl text-white text-sm shadow-lg transform active:scale-95 transition duration-200">Hitung Target Win</button>
                </form>
            </div>

        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="border-t border-gray-800/80 py-6 text-center text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono">
        MLBB Hero Tracker &copy; 2026 - Continuous Deployment via Vercel
    </footer>

</body>
</html>